  "text": "Another attractive feature of these Schrödinger boundaries is that in the pure Sch 5 case the V coordinate can be thought of as parametrizing the light like lines [CITATION_1] which in turn form the boundaries of the light cones of the space-time. The Galilean-like causal structure is then naturally inherited by boundaries that have V as a tangential coordinate.",
